Package com.geodesk.feature.match

Class MatcherCoder

java.lang.Object
com.clarisma.common.bytecode.Coder
com.clarisma.common.ast.ExpressionCoder
com.geodesk.feature.match.MatcherCoder
All Implemented Interfaces:
AstVisitor<Void>
public class MatcherCoder extends ExpressionCoder
A bytecode generator that produces a TagMatcher class for a given query string. Note that the matcher code does not verify the feature type; it is the caller's responsibility to only apply the TagMatcher to features of the appropriate type. This class relies on the ExpressionCoder base class to encode the expression tree of each TagClause. Only a subset of expressions are supported: BinaryExpression: - AND/OR - value EQ/NE to String, GlobalString or Double - value LT/LE/GT/GE Double - value StartsWith/EndsWith/MatchesRegex String - value IN/NOT_IN List of GlobalString UnaryExpression: - NOT
